Package: NicheDiv
Title: Tools for Ecological Niche Divergence Analyses
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Daniel", "Schönberger", email = "daniel@familie-schoenberger.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions for a DAPC-based niche divergence approach, including
    occurrence thinning, background filtering, variable transformation,
    environmental data extraction, and related preprocessing steps.
